tagline.en: Of the community, by the community, for the communtiy
tagline.zh: 社区共有，社区共治，社区共享

introduce.en: EOS.CYBEX is an experienced team dedicated to EOS project incubation and community development, aiming at providing a myriad of one-stop services for all DAPP developers based on the EOS platform, including testchains readily accessible to developers, and sophisticated test tools and services.
introduce.zh: EOS.CYBEX是一个专注于EOS项目孵化、生态运营的社区，旨在为EOS上的DAPP开发者提供一站式服务，其中包括测试链开发环境和最齐全的测试工具及服务。
